I recently ordered 4 boxes of these size syringes from Amazon and the product received had a Proposition 65 Cancer risk warning on the boxes. I want to make sure this will not occur if I begin ordering from your company.  Can you assure that this will not happen? If so I'll order my 6 boxes today.

Total Diabetes Supply: Great question! I want to make sure I give you the most accurate information, so I'll check in with my team. Since it's the weekend, I may not hear back until Monday, but I'll be sure to follow up with you as soon as I do!

Thank you so much! I couldn't believe it when I saw that warning on the box. All this after I found 90 out of 300 brand-new syringes to be contaminated. This was from 3 different companies as well. I don't know what's going on but I plan to be much more thorough and cautious moving forward. I look forward to hearing from you!

Total Diabetes Supply: You're welcome, and I completely understand your concern! I'm very sorry to hear about the issues you've experienced. Your safety is our top priority, and I'll keep you posted as soon as I have more information available.
